items.title: Fulmer to have surgery, out 3-4 months
items.summary: Tigers pitcher Michael Fulmer will have ulnar transposition surgery on Tuesday in Pensacola, Fla., after visiting Dr. James Andrews on Monday. The recovery time is three to four months.

items.title: Drama ahead as home-field races tighten
items.summary: So much for all those races being decided early. If the past month has proven anything about baseball, it's that you never really know what's going to happen, no matter how dominant or mortal a team looks.
